What:		/sys/class/iommu/<iommu>/arm-smmu-v3/stall
Date:		December 2017
KernelVersion:	??
Contact:	Jean-Philippe Brucker <jean-philippe.brucker@arm.com>
Description:
		If "enabled", stall model is supported by the SMMU and
		available to stall-capable devices. If "force", stall model is
		forced for all devices. If "disabled", stall model isn't
		available.

What:		/sys/class/iommu/<iommu>/arm-smmu-v3/httu
Date:		December 2017
KernelVersion:	??
Contact:	Jean-Philippe Brucker <jean-philippe.brucker@arm.com>
Description:
		Hardware Translation Table Update feature. "access+dirty",
		"access" or "none".

